text: John Benedict Eden, Baron Eden of Winton, (15 September 1925 – 23 May 2020) was a British Conservative politician. He was the Member of Parliament for Bournemouth West from 1954 to 1983. From 1983 to 2015, he was a member of the House of Lords.
